<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1919] libthrift depends on httpcore-4.1.3 (directly) and httpcore-4.1.4 (transitively)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1919</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I believe this is the same issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1693&quot; title=&quot;libthrift has dependency on two different versions of httpcore&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-1693&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-1693&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but with different versions.  There&apos;s a direct dependency on both httpclient and httpcore version 4.1.3 in thriftlib, but httpclient:4.1.3 has a dependency on httpcore:4.1.4.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are the dependencies Gradle shows me.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;\--- org.apache.thrift:libthrift:0.9.0
     +--- org.slf4j:slf4j-api:1.5.8
     +--- commons-lang:commons-lang:2.5
     +--- org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient:4.1.3
     |    +--- org.apache.httpcomponents:httpcore:4.1.4
     |    +--- commons-logging:commons-logging:1.1.1
     |    \--- commons-codec:commons-codec:1.4
     \--- org.apache.httpcomponents:httpcore:4.1.3 -&amp;gt; 4.1.4 (*)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a copy of the dependency resolution section of my Gradle build in case anyone needs a short term workaround.  The force option is what allows the direct dependency to be overridden to 4.1.4 (shown with a * in the above snippet).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;all {
    resolutionStrategy {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// fails when multiple versions of the same dependency exist (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; includes
&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// transitive dependencies)
&lt;/span&gt;        failOnVersionConflict()

        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// don&apos;t cache snapshot / changing modules
&lt;/span&gt;        cacheChangingModulesFor 0, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;seconds&apos;&lt;/span&gt;

        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// force httpcore to 4.1.4 to avoid version conflict
&lt;/span&gt;        force &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.apache.httpcomponents:httpcore:4.1.4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows x64 + Maven or Gradle.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
